<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to PropertyOS</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding-bottom: 30px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #8b5cf6;
    }
    .header h1 {
      color: #8b5cf6;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 32px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px 0;
    }
    .welcome-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #6366f1 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .welcome-box h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 24px;
    }
    .welcome-box p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 18px;
      opacity: 0.95;
    }
    .features {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .feature {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .feature-icon {
      font-size: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .feature h4 {
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
      color: #1f2937;
    }
    .feature p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #8b5cf6;
      color: white;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background-color: #7c3aed;
    }
    .temp-password {
      background-color: #fef3c7;
      border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
      padding: 15px 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .temp-password h4 {
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
      color: #92400e;
    }
    .temp-password code {
      background-color: white;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #1f2937;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 30px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>PropertyOS</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="welcome-box">
        <h2>Welcome, {{userName}}! üéâ</h2>
        <p>You're now part of {{organizationName}}</p>
      </div>

      <p>We're excited to have you on board! PropertyOS is designed to make property management simple and efficient for everyone.</p>

      <div class="features">
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">üè†</div>
          <h4>Property Management</h4>
          <p>Manage your properties with ease</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">üí≥</div>
          <h4>Online Payments</h4>
          <p>Pay rent securely online</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">üîß</div>
          <h4>Maintenance Requests</h4>
          <p>Submit and track requests</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">üìä</div>
          <h4>Real-time Updates</h4>
          <p>Stay informed instantly</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      {{#if temporaryPassword}}
      <div class="temp-password">
        <h4>üîë Your Temporary Password:</h4>
        <code>{{temporaryPassword}}</code>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; color: #92400e;">Please change this password after your first login.</p>
      </div>
      {{/if}}

      <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">Get Started ‚Üí</a>

      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance getting started, our support team is here to help. Just reply to this email or contact us through the app.</p>
      
      <p>Welcome again to the PropertyOS family!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} PropertyOS. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>This is an automated email, please do not reply.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>